OL,3,CWatch: Families emotional testimony as
OL,4,CCovid inquiry opens in Belfast
OL,6,FRelatives of people from Northern
OL,7,FIreland who died during the pandemic
OL,8,Fhave hailed the first sitting of the
OL,9,FUK Covid-19 Inquiry in Belfast as an
OL,10,F"important day".
OL,12,FA number of bereaved family members
OL,13,Fgathered outside the Clayton Hotel in
OL,14,FBelfast, holding photographs of their
OL,15,Floved ones ahead of the first hearing
OL,16,Fon Tuesday.
