OL,6,FThe UK-wide inquiry's hearings in
OL,7,FBelfast will run for three weeks and
OL,8,Fare designed to provide an opportunity
OL,9,Fto look in "depth" at the decisions
OL,10,Ftaken in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FIt opened with a 20 minute 'impact
OL,13,Fvideo' which showed the experiences of
OL,14,Fsome of those affected by the disease
OL,15,For lost their loved ones.
