OL,6,FThis module will investigate the
OL,7,Finitial response, central government
OL,8,Fdecision-making, political and civil
OL,9,Fservice performance as well as the
OL,10,Feffectiveness of relationships with
OL,11,Fgovernments in the devolved
OL,12,Fadministrations and local and
OL,13,Fvoluntary sectors.
OL,15,FIt will also assess decisions behind
OL,16,Flockdowns and other non-pharmaceutical
OL,17,Finterventions.
