OL,6,FA campaign group representing bereaved
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland families held the
OL,8,Fpublic gathering to coincide with the
OL,9,Ffirst day of the Belfast sittings.
OL,11,FBrenda Doherty, who lost her mother
OL,12,FRuth Burke, said:"This is a very, very
OL,13,Fimportant day for us here in Northern
OL,14,FIreland.
OL,16,F"Over the next three weeks we hope all
OL,17,Fthose who are here to give evidence do
OL,18,Fso with with truth and honesty and
OL,19,Fanswer questions without any
OL,20,Fhesitation.
